Provides: nginx, httpd, httpd-cgi
Conflicts: nginx, nginx-stable
Replaces: nginx, nginx-stable
Description: high performance web server and reverse proxy (mainline)
 nginx ("engine x") is a high performance web server, reverse proxy, and
 IMAP/POP3 proxy server. It is known for its stability, rich feature set,
 simple configuration, and low resource consumption.
 .
 This package is compiled from the nginx mainline release branch, which is
 updated roughly every one to two months and includes the latest features,
 bug fixes, and security fixes. The mainline branch always carries an odd
 minor version number (for example, 1.31.x).
